1988;;Distant Thunder;;American;;Rick Rosenthal;;John Lithgow, Ralph Macchio;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Distant_Thunder_(1988_film);;The film tells the story of troubled Vietnam war veteran Mark Lambert (John Lithgow), who, upon returning home from the war, alienates his wife and child by deserting them and moving away into the remote wilderness of Washington state.<br><br>After 10 years of living off the land and suffering from post-traumatic stress disorder, Mark Lambert decides to rejoin civilized society and find his now teenage son, who is living in Illinois. As an estranged father and recluse, Mark Lambert quickly finds himself unprepared for the changes that he must face.